      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This is a collector-grade example that has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment. The exterior paint is flawless, displaying a deep, glass-like luster free of swirl marks, rock chips, or imperfections, further protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the leather remains supple with zero bolster wear, and the factory scent persists. Every electronic component and interior switch operates with crisp, tactile precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having followed a rigorous maintenance schedule with all records organized in a comprehensive binder. It conveys with all original keys, the factory window sticker, and unused floor mats. For the buyer seeking a showroom-standard vehicle that feels as though it just rolled off the assembly line, this is the definitive choice.",
